{"tid":226481,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣可以增加專注力","createTime":"2017-05-02T14:09:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T07:14:37.000Z","uid":87428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2a4137493d3a8f0d536f3d5ecaeb94fa84a7404f","tid":226481,"uid":87428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T14:09:26.000Z","msg":"我份人做沒興趣既野 就極難專注<br />\n每次deadline assignment ,都勁辛苦<br />\n成日沒野做 戇居居咁開住個work 坐成日<br />\n都最後坐到凌晨三四點 先開始做到<br />\n當中其間成日同自己講食完飯先做<br />\n聽首歌先做, 做完乜乜先做<br />\n考試都係咁,又係溫唔到<br />\n明明聽日朝早考final ,但又係凌晨兩三點先溫到書<br />\n知道自己沒乜時間可以hea ,之後唔知點解上左電可以一野<br />\n溫哂,兩個鐘作三千字英文<br />\n改極都改唔到,以為自己早D 溫書就會溫到<br />\n<br />\nDSE 又係咁,人地成年前就溫,我就係考個日先凌晨12點先開始溫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好辛苦,我都唔想咁"},{"pid":"a7a7fb23d78514c8954e6fe70502b11253d5d8e5","tid":226481,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T14:10:31.000Z","msg":"無得救<br />\n利申:deadline fighter"},{"pid":"6fb05f18009b92486c481649716b8291db5c526a","tid":226481,"uid":49055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T14:10:52.000Z","msg":"打丁"},{"pid":"d754b1d9b7a1b996724f090c5ff0880fe1becffd","tid":226481,"uid":20899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T14:13:53.000Z","msg":"同你一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7354eabbfb5a6e6882fb02d9e91601ee52d88f16","tid":226481,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T14:40:45.000Z","msg":"認真，聽講藥房d聰明藥有幫助<br />\n不過頭盔先，未試過，自己唔敢但又想試，唔知有無效呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56cc68d32304b365234b00619aa230b627d42e0","tid":226481,"uid":70621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T14:42:51.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日溫溫下 做做下野會睇YouTube<br />\n一睇就幾粒鐘"},{"pid":"67e4d0261da66eb957cec634b80bd2019fac1526","tid":226481,